    <section id="about" class="section">
        <div class="container" style="padding-top:20px">
            <h4>About</h4>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="span12 offset1">
                    <div>
                        <h2><strong>MyDay</strong> Experienced Wellbeing Surveys</h2>
                        <p style="color:black">
                            MyDay is an internet-based survey study of wellbeing at work. A goal of the surveys is to measure the experience of workers in their day-to-day activities. MyDay was piloted in 2017 and is now being used to understand the impact of workspaces on the daily experience.
                            <br /><br />
                            MyDay is led by Professor Rhema Vaithianathan of Auckland University of Technology, New Zealand.
                            <br />
                            <br />
                            MyDay launched in 2017 to learn about the experienced wellbeing of trainee doctors in Wessex, England, in a study led by Auckland University of Technology, Health Education England (Working across Wessex) and Cass Business School (City, University of London).
                            <br />
                            <br />
                            <a href="@Url.Action("FAQs","Root")" style="color:teal;">Find out more about MyDay</a>.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- /.container -->
